          "Authors do an ex-post analysis of dropout at their university- Not ondly do they create a set of predictive models but also look to analyze factors that help explain Dropout.\n\nClass change is much more difficult to prediuct correctly than the otyher 2 classes. \n\nAuthors also look to optimize their C4.5 Decision Tree (which in this case, since its WeKA should be J48).\n\n",
