    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8052-861b-f3014ea93092",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Analyzing dropout in large datasets is difficult. Authors propose a non-parametric ML approach that handles large datasets well and is interpretable. Results of this approach show that performance in first year, personal and contextual variables play a key role in predicting dropout.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8052-861b-f3014ea93092",
        "parent": {
